{"word":"ἀποψάω","slug":"ἀποψάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀποψάω</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to wipe off</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <i>to wipe</i> or <i>rub off from oneself</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <a href='S:person, personal'>pers.</a> <i>to wipe clean</i>: — <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <i>to wipe oneself, wipe one's nose</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>; also, <el>ἀποψ. τὴν χεῖρα εἴς τι</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}